Package: g3viz
Type: Package
Title: Interactively Visualize Genetic Mutation Data using a Lollipop-Diagram
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Xin", "Guo", email = "g3viz.group@gmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3894-1693")),
    person("Rener", "Zhang", email = "g3viz.group@gmail.com", role = c("ctb"))
    )
Description: The g3viz package provides an interface to the 'g3-lollipop' JavaScript library. This enables the visualization of genetic mutation data. This package allows users to create interactive lollipop diagrams in RStudio or a web browser.
